%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20coauthor%20of%20the%20viral%20Citrini%20Research%20report%20that%20rattled%20markets%20shares%20the%20investing%20strategy%20to%20guard%20against%20AI%20disruption%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225760%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wall%20Street%20traders%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20New%20York%20Stock%20Exchange.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c2f58fe98a37a4841f336f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EXinhua%2F%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20finance%20pros%20who%20rattled%20markets%20with%20their%20AI%20thought%20experiment%20last%20month%20are%20out%20with%20a%20new%20update.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20writers%20built%20on%20their%20outlook%20for%20AI%20disruption%20that%20spooked%20investors.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECoauthor%20Alap%20Shah%20told%20Business%20Insider%20about%20his%20strategies%20for%20investors%20if%20the%20crisis%20they%20imagine%20plays%20out.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20know%20markets%20are%20on%20edge%20when%20a%20piece%20of%20fiction%20sends%20stocks%20tumbling.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20exactly%20what%20happened%20on%20February%2022%2C%20as%20tech%20stocks%20dropped%20on%20a%20blog%20post%20from%20a%20little-known%20market%20research%20firm%20called%20Citrini%20Research%20about%20how%20AI%20could%20disrupt%20markets%20and%20the%20economy%20by%202028.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report's%20coauthor%2C%20Alap%20Shah%2C%20says%20he%20did%20not%20expect%20the%20report%20to%20attract%20the%20attention%20it%20did.%20The%20Substack%20post%2C%20titled%20%26quot%3BThe%20Global%20Intelligence%20Crisis%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-ai-boom-recession-citrini-research-layoffs-jobs-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elaid%20out%20a%20vision%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20future%20in%20which%20AI%20leads%20to%20widespread%20white-collar%20job%20losses%2C%20a%20consumer-led%20recession%2C%20and%20a%20plunge%20in%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShah%20published%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Falapshah1.substack.com%2Fp%2Fthe-global-intelligence-crisis-part%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanother%20installment%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20sharing%20more%20thoughts%20about%20what%20he%20expects%20to%20see%20from%20the%20AI%20boom.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThree%20weeks%20ago%2C%20the%20essays%20we%20authored%20clearly%20struck%20a%20nerve%2C%26quot%3B%20Shah%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feconomists-business-leaderss-react-citrini-report-ai-recession-stock-crash-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eresponse%3C%2Fa%3E%20exceeded%20anything%20we%20anticipated%2C%20and%20the%20market%20impact%20was%20neither%20our%20expectation%20nor%20our%20intent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShah%20laid%20out%20what%20he%20calls%20the%20%26quot%3Bsynthetic%20short%2C%26quot%3B%20essentially%20a%20system-level%20bet%20against%20the%20human-driven%20economy%20that%20will%20emerge%20as%20AI%20overtakes%20entire%20industries%2C%20compromising%20economic%20growth%20in%20the%20ways%20he%20and%20Citrini%20laid%20out%20in%20the%20first%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUltimately%2C%20what%20we're%20saying%20is%2C%20'hey%2C%20this%20short%20exists.'%20We%20want%20to%20be%20more%20explicit%20in%20calling%20it%20out%2C%20and%20then%20we%20want%20to%20start%20talking%20about%20policy%20solutions%20that%20can%20ensure%20that%20instead%20of%20a%20real%20risk%20of%20a%20crash%2C%20we%20figure%20it%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20scenarios%20outlined%20by%20Shah%20and%20Citrini%20pose%20a%20unique%20challenge%20for%20investors.%20The%20AI%20trade%20essentially%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-markets-ai-tech-layoff-trade-first-trade-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epropped%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20stock%20market%20for%20three%20years%20after%20the%20debut%20of%20ChatGPT%2C%20as%20companies%20scaled%20AI%20endeavors%20and%20Wall%20Street%20cheered%20them%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20the%20scenarios%20imagined%20by%20Shah%20and%20Citrini%20play%20out%20in%20any%20way%20similar%20to%20how%20their%20viral%20report%20predicted%2C%20AI%20will%20ultimately%20be%20a%20drag%20on%20markets.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20AI%20complex%20and%20the%20consumer%20economy%20are%20increasingly%20on%20opposite%20sides%20of%20the%20same%20trade.%20That%20is%20not%20sustainable%20and%20is%20not%20something%20that%20the%20AI%20complex%2C%20investors%20or%20society%20should%20want%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Falapshah1.substack.com%2Fp%2Fthe-global-intelligence-crisis-part%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20latest%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20reads.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShah%2C%20a%20veteran%20of%20the%20financial%20and%20tech%20spaces%2C%20shared%20some%20strategies%20for%20investors%20to%20guard%20against%20these%20losses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20view%2C%20the%20most%20strategic%20way%20is%20to%20still%20be%20long%20AI%2C%20specifically%20the%20companies%20powering%20the%20revolution%2C%20primarily%20those%20building%20semiconductors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20a%20high%20level%2C%20the%20cleanest%20way%20to%20get%20access%20is%20to%20buy%20semiconductor%20stocks%2C%20because%20that%20is%20the%20underlying%20substrate%20through%20which%20all%20the%20AI%20is%20built%2C%20as%20well%20as%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20technology%20complex%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShah%20highlighted%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fvaneck_semiconductor_etf_cert_deposito_arg_repr_002-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EVanEck%20Semiconductor%20ETF%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20cleanest%20way%20to%20gain%20access%20to%20booming%20AI%20chipmakers%20with%20relatively%20lower%20risk%20than%20buying%20single%20names.%20He%20sees%20semis%20in%20stark%20contrast%20to%20the%20software%20industry%2C%20which%20he%20thinks%20poses%20a%20clear%20risk%20for%20investors%20due%20to%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-cowork-legal-plugin-publishing-stocks-legalzoom-thomson-reuters-relx-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20disruptions%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20advice%20for%20investors%20trying%20to%20tell%20the%20AI%20winners%20from%20the%20losers%20is%20to%20look%20closely%20at%20where%20a%20company's%20revenue%20comes%20from.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20a%20company%20gets%20its%20revenue%20from%20the%20AI%20complex%2C%20like%20semiconductors%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20that%20is%20obviously%20an%20AI%20winner%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20stated.%20%26quot%3BIf%20a%20company%20gets%20its%20revenue%20from%20consumers%2C%20there%20probably%20will%20be%20a%20lot%20of%20risk%2C%20because%20the%20consumer%20is%20going%20to%20be%20under%20pressure.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShah%20added%20that%20if%20the%20scenario%20they%20envisioned%20comes%20to%20pass%2C%20he%20sees%20high%20risk%20for%20companies%20in%20the%20financial%20services%20sector%20and%20other%20intermediaries%20that%20facilitate%20transactions%20between%20humans.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20sorts%20of%20businesses%20we%20think%20are%20going%20to%20be%20under%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%2C%20because%20AI%20makes%20the%20value%20of%20intermediation%20a%20lot%20lower%20and%20agents%20can%20transact%20with%20other%20agents%20at%20much%2C%20much%20lower%20costs%20than%20humans%20transacting%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcitrini-research-ai-report-alap-shah-stock-market-outlook-economy-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774448880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c3d27c5b58f1f0f9336ee9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcitrini-research-ai-report-alap-shah-stock-market-outlook-economy-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Alap%20Shah%2C%20who%20coauthored%20last%20month's%20viral%20AI%20thought%20experiment%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20about%20what%20he%20sees%20ahead%20and%20how%20to%20play%20the%20coming%20disruption.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sobrient%40insider.com%20(Samuel%20O'Brient)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcitrini-research-ai-report-alap-shah-stock-market-outlook-economy-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20asks%20judge%20to%20recuse%20herself%20in%20Tesla%20shareholder%20case%2C%20saying%20she%20hearted%20post%20about%20him%20losing%20a%20lawsuit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224140%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elon%20Musk%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b3c75fa96e437d6eb841bd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222760%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElon%20Musk%20said%20that%20he%20is%20looking%20at%20xAI's%20interview%20history%20to%20scan%20for%20missed%20talent.%3Cp%3EFabrice%20COFFRINI%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EElon%20Musk's%20lawyers%20have%20asked%20Delaware%20Chancery%20Court's%20top%20judge%20to%20recuse%20herself%20from%20a%20case.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20say%20she%20hearted%20a%20LinkedIn%20post%20criticizing%20him.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20judge%20says%20she%20never%20read%20the%20post%20and%20reported%20her%20emoji%20reaction%20as%20%26quot%3Bsuspicious%20activity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Delaware%20judge%20overseeing%20a%20lawsuit%20against%20Elon%20Musk%20has%20appeared%20in%20at%20least%20one%20LinkedIn%20search%20%E2%80%94%20from%20his%20lawyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAttorneys%20for%20the%20Tesla%20CEO%20have%20asked%20Chancellor%20Kathaleen%20McCormick%20to%20recuse%20herself%20from%20a%20shareholder%20lawsuit%20against%20him%20because%20of%20her%20reactions%20to%20a%20LinkedIn%20post%20criticizing%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20light%20of%20the%20Court's%20recent%20public%20support%20of%20LinkedIn%20posts%20that%20create%20a%20perception%20of%20bias%20against%20Mr.%20Musk%20in%20these%20cases%2C%20recusal%20is%20necessary%20and%20warranted%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote%20in%20a%20Tuesday%20night%20court%20filing.%20%26quot%3BThese%20cases%20should%20be%20re-assigned%20to%20another%20random-drawn%20judicial%20officer%20of%20this%20Court.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20recusal%20motion%20was%20filed%20in%20a%20set%20of%20lawsuits%20brought%20by%20Tesla%20shareholders%20who%20allege%20Musk%20lied%20about%20selling%20his%20Tesla%20shares%20in%20the%20lead-up%20to%20his%202022%20purchase%20of%20Twitter%2C%20enabling%20him%20to%20profit%20illegally.%20Musk%20has%20denied%20wrongdoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Tuesday%20filing%2C%20McCormick%20reacted%20positively%20to%20a%20LinkedIn%20post%20from%20a%20lawyer%20who%20won%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-decoy-tesla-distracted-photographers-twitter-trial-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20separate%20case%20in%20California%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20accusing%20Musk%20of%20misleading%20Twitter%20shareholders.%20The%20post%20celebrated%20the%20law%20firm%20that%20brought%20the%20case%20for%20%26quot%3Bstanding%20up%20for%20the%20little%20guy%20against%20the%20richest%20man%20in%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk's%20attorneys%20said%20McCormick%2C%20who%20has%20ruled%20against%20Musk%20in%20other%20high-profile%20cases%2C%20put%20effort%20into%20reacting%20to%20one%20of%20the%20posts%20criticizing%20him.%20She%20chose%20to%20react%20with%20%26quot%3BSupport%26quot%3B%20rather%20than%20a%20mere%20%26quot%3BLike%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20particular%20reaction%20selected%20by%20Chancellor%20McCormick's%20account%20%E2%80%94%20'Support%2C'%20symbolized%20by%20a%20heart%20hovering%20in%20an%20outstretched%20hand%E2%80%94%20requires%20deliberate%20selection%2C%20an%20effort%20beyond%20clicking%20the%20generic%20'like'%20button%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BOf%20about%20121%20reactions%20to%20the%20post%2C%2093%20chose%20the%20default%20'like'%20and%20only%20one%20selected%20the%20outstretched%20heart%20in%20hand%20to%20'support'%20the%20post.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221524%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22kate%20mccormick%20linkedin%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c3753e5b58f1f0f9336e4c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221082%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDelaware%20Chancellor%20Kate%20McCormick%20put%20effort%20into%20reacting%20to%20a%20LinkedIn%20post%20criticizing%20Elon%20Musk%20by%20not%20simply%20%26quot%3Bliking%26quot%3B%20it%2C%20his%20lawyers%20say.%3Cp%3EDelaware%20Court%20of%20Chancery%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMcCormick's%20LinkedIn%20account%20appeared%20to%20be%20deactivated%20on%20March%2023%2C%20the%20lawyers%20wrote.%20Business%20Insider%20was%20unable%20to%20locate%20her%20account.%20McCormick's%20chambers%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20own%20letter%20dated%20Tuesday%2C%20McCormick%20said%20she%20didn't%20recall%20even%20seeing%20the%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLinkedIn%20recently%20reported%20that%20I%20hit%20the%20heart-in-hand%20icon%20intended%20to%20show%20a%20sign%20of%20'support'%20concerning%20a%20LinkedIn%20post%20about%20Mr.%20Musk%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BI%20do%20not%20'support'%20the%20post.%20I%20also%20have%20not%20read%20the%20post%2C%20aside%20from%20the%20text%20visible%20in%20the%20screenshot%20that%20was%20sent%20by%20text%20to%20me%20last%20night.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20said%20she%20%26quot%3Breported%20the%20suspicious%20activity%20to%20LinkedIn%26quot%3B%20and%20was%20then%20locked%20out%20of%20her%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcCormick%20serves%20as%20the%20chancellor%20%E2%80%94%20effectively%2C%20the%20chief%20judge%20%E2%80%94%20of%20the%20Delaware%20Court%20of%20Chancery.%20She%20has%20previously%20overseen%20two%20other%20cases%20involving%20Musk%2C%20neither%20of%20which%20turned%20out%20as%20he%20hoped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20she%20oversaw%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-twitter-lawsuit-to-enforce-acquisition-takeover-deal-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20case%20Twitter%20brought%20against%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20force%20him%20to%20go%20through%20with%20his%20purchase%20of%20the%20social%20media%20company%20after%20he%20tried%20to%20back%20out.%20After%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftwitter-upper-hand-elon-musk-court-battle-hearing-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMcCormick%20ruled%20in%20Twitter's%20favor%3C%2Fa%3E%20early%20in%20the%20litigation%2C%20Musk%20agreed%20to%20go%20through%20with%20the%20purchase%20before%20the%20case%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcCormick%20also%20sided%20with%20shareholders%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjudge-strikes-down-elon-musk-tesla-compensation-pay-package-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%202024%20ruling%20that%20struck%20down%20Musk's%20%2455%20billion%20Tesla%20pay%20package%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20himself%2C%20though%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelaware-court-reinstates-elon-musk-55-billion-tesla-pay-package-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDelaware's%20Supreme%20Court%20later%20overturned%20her%20ruling%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcCormick's%20decision%20spurred%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-start-shifting-tesla-state-incorporation-to-texas-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMusk%20to%20move%20his%20companies%20from%20Delaware%20to%20Texas%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20has%20become%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flist-corporations-leaving-delaware-elon-musk-spacex-tesla-dropbox-roblox-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20minor%20trend%20in%20the%20business%20world%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk's%20attorneys%20said%20the%20LinkedIn%20shenanigans%20extended%20throughout%20McCormick's%20chambers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20filing%2C%20they%20said%20a%20member%20of%20McCormick's%20staff%20%26quot%3Bliked%26quot%3B%20a%20LinkedIn%20post%20from%20an%20attorney%20who%20posted%20a%20screenshot%20of%20a%20news%20article%20about%20Musk's%20testimony%20in%20the%20California%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20case%2C%20the%20now-X%20Corp.%20CEO%20testified%20that%20he%20believed%20McCormick%20was%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20biased%26quot%3B%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20many%20people%20who%20should%20be%20so%20deeply%20ashamed%20of%20themselves%20seem%20incapable%20of%20being%20so%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20think%20it's%20great%20for%20civil%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20attorney%20who%20posted%20the%20screenshot%20wrote%20in%20the%20LinkedIn%20post%20that%20was%20%26quot%3Bliked%26quot%3B%20by%20a%20member%20of%20the%20judge's%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-misled-twitter-investors-prior-to-purchase-jury-finds-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMusk%20lost%20the%20case%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-delaware-judge-recusal-linkedin-heart-tesla-shareholders-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774448711000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c3ef665b58f1f0f9336fbf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-delaware-judge-recusal