0had%20to%20make%20tough%20decisions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20tradeoffs%20were%20difficult%2C%20but%20I%20would%20definitely%20do%20it%20again.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20most%20of%20my%20career%2C%20I%20was%20very%20good%20at%20earning%20money%20and%20very%20bad%20at%20enjoying%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20years%20in%20high-pressure%20roles%3A%20mergers%20and%20acquisitions%20in%20Mexico%2C%20a%20hedge%20fund%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleave-nyc-miami-retire-early-saving-unexpected-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20capital%20markets%20in%20London.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20paper%2C%20the%20trajectory%20looked%20impressive.%20In%20practice%2C%20the%20life%20behind%20it%20felt%20increasingly%20hollow.%20I%20was%20billing%20hours%20I%20did%20not%20have.%20The%20hustle%20life%20was%20killing%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20do%20something%20about%20it.%20I%20took%20a%20break%20from%20life%2C%20recharged%20and%20reconnected%20with%20myself%2C%20and%20transitioned%20into%20a%20more%20balanced%20life.%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjob-seeker-landed-job-cold-emailing-the-ceo-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elanded%20a%20new%20job%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20came%20with%20a%20significant%20pay%20cut.%20I%20was%20making%20a%20third%20less%20than%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20itself%20felt%20romantic%2C%20but%20what%20no%20one%20prepared%20me%20for%20was%20what%20came%20after.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22013a85d6-667f-47fa-a908-2ba882b98426%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20couldn't%20comfortably%20afford%20life%20in%20London%20anymore%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20making%20the%20decision%2C%20I%20built%20a%20careful%20budget.%20I%20accounted%20for%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-luxury-rents-have-gone-up-new-york-london-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELondon%20rent%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20utilities%2C%20groceries%2C%20transport%2C%20and%20the%20occasional%20dinner%20out.%20It%20was%20the%20kind%20of%20spreadsheet%20that%20gives%20you%20confidence%20because%20it%20looks%20thorough%20and%20rational.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20I%20failed%20to%20properly%20account%20for%20was%20the%20texture%20of%20daily%20life%20in%20an%20expensive%20city%20like%20London%20when%20you%20are%20no%20longer%20earning%20a%20salary%20that%20absorbs%20every%20mistake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20costs%20I%20had%20not%20modeled%20were%20rarely%20dramatic.%20They%20were%20cumulative%3A%20a%20weekend%20trip%20you%20do%20not%20want%20to%20skip%2C%20a%20dinner%20with%20friends%20you%20cannot%20easily%20split%20differently.%20a%20birthday%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famtrak-usa-rail-pass-what-to-know-surprises-frequent-traveler-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrain%20ticket%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20flight%20home.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20these%20things%20feels%20extravagant%2C%20but%20together%20they%20quietly%20reshape%20the%20financial%20equation.%20The%20gap%20between%20%26quot%3BI%20can%20afford%20this%20city%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BI%20can%20afford%20this%20city%20comfortably%26quot%3B%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20wider%20than%20I%20had%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20also%20a%20psychological%20dimension%20to%20earning%20less%20that%20I%20underestimated.%20Not%20shame%2C%20exactly.%20I%20had%20already%20made%20peace%20with%20the%20title%20change%20before%20accepting%20the%20role.%20But%20there%20was%20a%20subtle%20awareness%20of%20constraint%20that%20had%20not%20existed%20before.%20Small%20decisions%20carried%20slightly%20more%20weight%2C%20and%20I%20noticed%20prices%20in%20ways%20I%20had%20not%20previously.%20It%20was%20not%20a%20crisis%2C%20just%20a%20different%20relationship%20with%20money%2C%20and%20one%20that%20took%20time%20to%20recalibrate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e68c