ts%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20having%20to%20sleep%20in%20the%20airport%20because%20of%20long%20delays%20in%20security%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmily%20Calandriello%2C%20an%20NYC%20resident%20who%20was%20traveling%20with%20her%20husband%20from%20JFK%20Airport%20to%20Costa%20Rica%20this%20week%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20she%20missed%20her%20flight%20after%20nearly%20getting%20caught%20in%20what%20she%20described%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bstampede%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20security%20line.%20She%20ended%20up%20staying%20the%20night%20in%20the%20airport%20and%20taking%20a%20flight%20out%20the%20next%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETSA%20agents%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-big-airports-tsa-worker-shortage-long-waits-government-shutdown-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewithout%20pay%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20weeks%20due%20to%20the%20partial%20government%20shutdown%2C%20and%20many%20are%20calling%20out%20of%20work%2C%20leading%20to%20staffing%20shortages%20and%20long%20lines%20for%20travelers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20now%2C%20there's%20no%20clear%20path%20on%20when%20these%20issues%20will%20be%20resolved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20House%20and%20the%20Senate%20are%20due%20to%20meet%20on%20Friday%20before%20a%20two-week%20recess.%20If%20funding%20for%20the%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security%20is%20not%20resolved%2C%20it%20could%20mean%20another%20two%20weeks%20of%20delayed%20pay%20for%20TSA%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-war-oil-price-shock-commentary-bob-mcnally-nightmare-forecast-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erising%20oil%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20pushing%20airfares%20up.%20The%20price%20of%20Brent%20crude%20oil%20has%20spiked%20by%20as%20much%20as%2060%25%20since%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-war-taco-trade-trump-stock-market-oil-prices-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estart%20of%20the%20Ir