0live%20in%20Mexico%2C%20want%20to%20visit%20family%20in%20Florida%20but%20are%20afraid%20to%20fly%20with%20all%20the%20TSA%20delays.%3Cp%3ESilvia%20and%20Greg%20Lupone%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20travelers%20are%20opting%20to%20stay%20closer%20to%20home%20or%20choosing%20trains%20and%20cars%20over%20flights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGreg%20Lupone%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Silvia%2C%20who%20live%20in%20Cozumel%2C%20Mexico%2C%20wanted%20to%20visit%20his%2093-year-old%20father%20in%20Pensacola%2C%20Florida%2C%20this%20month%2C%20but%20feel%20it's%20too%20risky%20to%20book%20anything%20because%20of%20the%20TSA%20chaos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20go%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20just%20too%20afraid%20to%20book.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20typically%20visit%20a%20few%20times%20a%20year%2C%20booking%20about%20a%20month%20or%20so%20in%20advance%2C%20and%20fly%20from%20Cozumel%20International%20Airport%20with%20a%20layover%20in%20Houston%2C%20Atlanta%2C%20or%20Dallas.%20But%20the%20airports%20in%20Houston%20and%20Atlanta%20have%20seen%20some%20of%20the%20longest%20TSA%20wait%20times%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20security%20line%20is%20two%20to%20three%20hours%20long%2C%20we%20miss%20our%20connecting%20flight%20in%20Dallas%2C%26quot%3B%20Silvia%20Lupone%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20miss%20our%20flight%2C%20we%20waste%20a%20whole%20day%20with%20Dad.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20hoping%20to%20book%20a%20trip%20soon.%20If%20the%20partial%20shutdown%20ends%20and%20TSA%20operations%20resume%20normally%2C%20Greg%20Lupone%20said%20they'd%20book%20%26quot%3Bimmediately.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20puts%20our%20lives%20on%20hold%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BWith%20elderly%20parents%2C%20you%20only%20have%20so%20many%20more%20visits%20left.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Portrait%20of%20a%20woman%20with%20the%20beach%20in%20the%20distance.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c3532de98a37a4841f353a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMickey%20Lyons%2C%20based%20in%20Detroit%2C%20chose%20to%20avoid%20airport%20chaos%20and%20drive%20to%20Indianapolis%20and%20Louisville.%3Cp%3EMickey%20Lyons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Mickey%20Lyons%2C%20a%2053-year-old%20freelance%20journalist%20and%20lecturer%20based%20in%20Detroit%2C%20had%20plans%20to%20meet%20up%20with%20friends%20in%20Indianapolis%20and%20Louisville.%20Normally%2C%20she%20would%20have%20flown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20of%20the%20recent%20airport%20chaos%2C%20I%20chose%20to%20drive%20both%20times%20%E2%80%94%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20fuel%20prices%20skyrocketed%20halfway%20through%20the%20month%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20month%2C%20it%20made%20a%20little%20more%20sense%20because%20the%20chaos%20at%20the%20airport%20was%20already%20starting%2C%20but%20fuel%20prices%20weren't%20crazy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20had%20already%20committed%20to%20driving%20to%20Kentucky.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20in%20the%20days%20I%20was%20there%2C%20fuel%20prices%20jumped%20a%20%241%20a%20gallon%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20Average%20US%20gasoline%20prices%20are%20up%20to%20%243.98%20per%20gallon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELyons%20said%20the%20uncertainty%20has%20also%20changed%20how%20she%20books%20travel.%20Normally%2C%20she%20books%20at%20least%20three%20months%20in%20advance%2C%20but%20now%20she's%20holding%20off%20to%20see%20if%20prices%20drop%20%E2%80%94%20and%20reconsidering%20how%20she%20gets%20places.%20She%20said%20she%20needs%20to%20be%20in%20Montreal%20by%20May%202%20but%20is%20delaying%20booking%20in%20case%20costs%20come%20down%2C%20giving%20herself%20until%20April%201%20to%20decide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can't%20believe%20I'm%20saying%20this%2C%20but%20I'm%20considering%20driving%20across%20the%20border%20to%20Windsor%2C%20Ontario%2C%20and%20taking%20a%2012-hour%20train%20ride%20to%20Montreal%20rather%20than%20deal%20with%20airport%20hassles%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225326277f-a13d-4737-8b4b-fcf6a2f7067c%5C%22%3EThe%20mini%20break%20isn't%20going%20away%2C%20it's%20just%20changing%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20odds%20are%20stacked%20against%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhen-to-book-summer-flights-rising-oil-prices-experts-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20travelers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20their%20insatiable%20demand%20for%20travel%20has%20not%20been%20dented%20so%20much%20as%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClint%20Henderson%2C%20managing%20editor%20of%20The%20Points%20Guy%2C%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bwe%20have%20seen%20very%20little%20evidence%20of%20any%20letup%20in%20demand%20for%20spring%20break%2C%20summer%2C%20or%20even%20spontaneous%20trips.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20Henderson%20expects%20fares%20to%20continue%20rising%20as%20oil%20prices%20rise%2C%20there%20are%20still%20deals%20to%20be%20had%2C%20he%20said%20%E2%80%94%20as%20long%20as%20you're%20willing%20to%20dig.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20just%20getting%20harder%20to%20find.%20Today%20we%20learned%20of%20a%20Delta%20flash%20sale%20with%20one-way%20business%20class%20availability%20to%20Seoul%20for%20as%20few%20as%2089%2C000%20Delta%20SkyMiles%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20That's%20equivalent%20to%20around%20%241%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20advises%20travelers%20to%20use%20Google%20Flights%20Explore%20to%20find%20the%20cheapest%20flights%20and%20to%20choose%20countries%20where%20the%20US%20dollar%20is%20strong%2C%20so%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20penny%20pinch%20when%20you%20get%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20higher%20end%20of%20travel%2C%20customers%20are%20less%20fazed%20about%20rising%20fuel%20costs%20and%20more%20about%20the%20%26quot%3Bunpredictability%20and%20hassle%20at%20the%20airport%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Lucie%20Kittel%2C%20founder%20of%20Domino%20Travel%2C%20a%20luxury%20travel%20agency%20based%20in%20Connecticut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20mini%20break%20isn't%20going%20away%2C%20it's%20just%20changing.%20I'm%20booking%20more%20high-end%20getaways%20within%20driving%20distance%20%E2%80%94%20clients%20still%20want%20that%20escape%2C%20just%20without%20the%20stress%20of%20flying%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELaReau%20said%20her%20road%20trip%20home%20from%20Colorado%20to%20Oklahoma%20was%20a%20success%2C%20and%20she's%20starting%20to%20think%20about%20where%20else%20she%20can%20drive%20to%20when%20she%20next%20has%20time%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYellowstone%20is%20one%20option%20she's%20considering%2C%20about%2010%20hours%20away%20and%20somewhere%20she's%20never%20been.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20travel%20several%20times%20a%20year.%20If%20I%20have%20time%20off%2C%20I'm%20usually%20going%20somewhere.%20But%20these%20prices%20are%20insane%2C%20and%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20spend%20on%20one%20trip%20when%20I%20can%20normally%20take%20two%20or%20three%20trips%20for%20the%20same%20cost%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspontaneous-travel-weekend-trip-getaways-tsa-chaos-oil-prices-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774445350000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c2f902e98a37a4841f338b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspontaneous-travel-weekend-trip-getaways-tsa-chaos-oil-prices-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rising%20oil%20prices%20and%20long%20security%20lines%20at%20US%20airports%20are%20making%20spontaneous%20trips%20feel%20more%20expensive%20and%20less%20appealing.%22%2C%22au