-ccpa-126032501028_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20consumer%20protection%20body%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20such%20levies%20cannot%20be%20added%20automatically%2C%20calling%20them%20unfair%20trade%20practices%2C%20and%20warned%20that%20violations%20would%20invite%20strict%20action%20under%20the%20law%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Frestaurants-cannot-add-lpg-surcharge-to-bill-ccpa-126032501028_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Frestaurants-cannot-add-lpg-surcharge-to-bill-ccpa-126032501028_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Frestaurants-cannot-add-lpg-surcharge-to-bill-ccpa-126032501028_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20startup%20made%20AI%20agents%20to%20manage%20construction%20projects%20like%20data%20centers.%20See%20the%20pitch%20deck%20it%20used%20to%20raise%20%249%20million.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227704%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Krane%20founder%20and%20CEO%20Eshan%20Jayamanne%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c395c15b58f1f0f9336e65%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225139%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEshan%20Jayamanne%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Krane.%3Cp%3EKrane%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EKrane%20raised%20%249%20million%20for%20its%20AI%20agents%20that%20handle%20construction%20supply%20chain%20tasks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEshan%20Jayamanne%2C%20Krane's%20CEO%2C%20said%20about%20a%20third%20of%20its%20work%20is%20with%20data%20center%20construction%20projects.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECheck%20out%20the%20nine-page%20pitch%20deck%20that%20Krane%20used%20to%20secure%20the%20seed%20funding.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EKrane%2C%20a%20startup%20building%20AI%20software%20for%20construction%20supply%20chains%2C%20has%20raised%20%249%20million%20in%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20San%20Francisco-based%20startup%20has%20developed%20AI%20agents%20that%20help%20construction%20teams%20manage%20materials%20procurement%20and%20delivery%20for%20projects%20such%20as%20data%20centers%2C%20healthcare%20facilities%2C%20and%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20platform%20pulls%20in%20data%20from%20spreadsheets%2C%20project%20schedules%2C%20and%20supplier%20communications%20into%20a%20single%20system.%20It%20then%20uses%20AI%20agents%20to%20automate%20tasks%20such%20as%20tracking%20orders%2C%20following%20up%20with%20vendors%20by%20phone%20or%20email%2C%20and%20reconciling%20invoices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEshan%20Jayamanne%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Krane%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20his%20company's%20platform%20typically%20starts%20by%20identifying%20the%20equipment%20and%20materials%20specified%20in%20a%20construction%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20we%20look%20at%20'what%20are%20all%20my%20quotes%20across%20all%20my%20suppliers%2C%20and%20who%20can%20I%20actually%20work%20with'%20by%20comparing%20lead%20times%2C%20by%20comparing%20requirements%20for%20the%20spec.%20This%20is%20where%20AI%20comes%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20has%20created%20multiple%20AI%20agents%20that%20specialize%20in%20different%20areas%20of%20the%20supply%20chain%2C%20such%20as%20deliveries%20and%20flagging%20supply%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJayamanne%2C%20a%20former%20engineer%20and%20construction%20operator%20who%20worked%20on%20data%20center%20projects%2C%20founded%20the%20company%20in%202023.%20It%20aims%20to%20reduce%20delays%20in%20construction%20projects%20and%20prevent%20them%20from%20going%20over%20budget%2C%20and%20integrates%20with%20existing%20construction%20tools%20like%20Autodesk%20and%20Procore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20half%20of%20Krane's%20customers%20are%20healthcare%20projects%2C%20and%20around%20a%20third%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-center-locations-us-map-ai-boom-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edata%20center%20buildouts%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Jayamanne%20said.%20Data%20centers%20are%20complex%20projects%20that%20can%20be%20held%20up%20by%20any%20delays%20to%20critical%20equipment%2C%20such%20as%20generators%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConstruction%20tech%20has%20become%20increasingly%20competitive%2C%20and%20companies%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrunk-tools-funding-construction-ai-series-b-pitch-deck-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrunkTools%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Mastt%20are%20also%20leaning%20into%20AI%20agents.%20While%20construction%20has%20historically%20been%20slower%20than%20other%20industries%20to%20adopt%20software%20tools%2C%20Jayamanne%20says%20that's%20no%20longer%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20LLM%20moment%20has%20changed%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20large%20language%20models%2C%20the%20technology%20underpinning%20AI%20like%20ChatGPT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJayamanne%20said%20that%20humans%20are%20%26quot%3Bin%20the%20loop%26quot%3B%20to%20approve%20the%20decisions%20of%20Krane's%20AI%20agents%2C%20but%20its%20voice%20agents%20have%20greater%20autonomy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup's%20seed%20round%20was%20co-led%20by%20Glasswing%20Ventures%20and%20Link%20Ventures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20funding%20will%20be%20used%20to%20expand%20its%20product%20and%20add%20new%20features%2C%20including%20tools%20aimed%20at%20subcontractors%20and%20additional%20automation%20for%20procurement%20and%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20really%20focused%20on%20raising%20'just%20enough'%20because%20larger%20rounds%20don't%20make%20sense%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20companies%20like%20his%20can%20use%20AI%20to%20operate%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiny-