3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EOura%20Ring%20fans%20are%20spending%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20to%20bling%20up%20their%20wearable%20rings%20with%20diamond%20jackets.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFour%20US-based%20upscale%20jewelers%20said%20demand%20for%20these%20glitzy%20jackets%20has%20jumped%20this%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20ring%20jackets%20are%20often%20adorned%20with%20diamonds%20and%20can%20cost%20up%20to%20%2410%2C000.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDawn%20McKenna%2C%20the%2057-year-old%20CEO%20of%20a%20luxury%20real%20estate%20company%20based%20in%20Chicago%2C%20started%20focusing%20on%20wellness%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFriends%20had%20told%20her%20to%20get%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhabit-burger-ceo-daily-routine-oura-ring-workouts-preserve-energy-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOura%20Ring%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20track%20her%20health%2C%20but%20she%20was%20initially%20put%20off%20because%20of%20its%20appearance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20too%20vain.%20I%20think%20that%20thing%20is%20so%20%E2%80%94%20God%20bless%20%E2%80%94%20ugly%2C%20that%20I%20cannot%20wear%20that%20thing%2C%20I%20just%20can't%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20McKenna%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20where%20Florida-based%20fine%20jeweler%20Henri%20No%C3%ABl%20comes%20in.%20The%20store's%20founder%2C%20Vivian%20Grimes%2C%20told%20McKenna%20she%20could%20make%20her%20a%20diamond-encrusted%20jacket%20to%20go%20over%20the%20ring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20McKenna%2C%20it%20was%20a%20no-brainer.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20rare%20that%20something%20can%20be%20beautiful%2C%20but%20good%20for%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20will%20help%20me%20stay%20accountable%20and%20do%20all%20the%20things%20I'm%20supposed%20to%20be%20doing.%20And%20I'm%20excited%20about%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20finished%20piece%2C%20which%20she%20expects%20to%20receive%20next%20month%2C%20will%20be%20a%20%246%2C495%2014k%20gold%20jacket%20set%20with%20three%20natural%20diamonds%20that%20transforms%20her%20smart%20ring%20into%20a%20chunky%20cocktail%20ring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221206%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hand%20with%20red%20manicured%20nails%20wearing%20four%20gold%20pieces%20of%20jewelry%2C%20including%20an%20Oura%20Ring%20jacket%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20diamond%20encrusted%20bracelet.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69bab75875bee4e0ee55d93c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222144%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHenri%20No%C3%ABl%20sells%20custom%20Oura%20Ring%20jackets%2C%20pictured%20on%20the%20index%20finger%2C%20starting%20from%20%242%2C800.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Henri%20No%C3%ABl%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20the%20first%20jacket%20Grimes%20has%20designed.%20She%20initially%20came%20up%20with%20the%20idea%20last%20September%20during%20a%20client%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20then%20posted%20an%20image%20of%20the%20design%20to%20her%20Instagram%20and%20TikTok%20in%20early%20March.%20Since%20then%2C%20she's%20received%2040%20enquiries%20for%20custom%20Oura%20Ring%20jackets%2C%20and%20said%20new%20requests%20are%20coming%20in%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe's%20now%20launching%20a%20new%20collection%20of%20Oura%20Ring%20jackets%2C%20starting%20at%20%243%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225c3b5c60-936a-4310-a375-b50ef110c5a6%5C%22%3EWearables%2C%20but%20make%20them%20sparkly%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGrimes%20is%20not%20the%20only%20high-end%20jeweler%20that's%20riding%20the%20Oura%20Ring%20jacket%20wave.%20Three%20other%20US-based%20fine%20jewelers%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20demand%20for%20these%20glitzy%20jackets%20has%20jumped%20this%20year%2C%20with%20customers%20requesting%20bespoke%20designs%2C%20and%20some%20jewelers%20making%20these%20a%20permanent%20fixture%20in%20their%20collections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20only%20a%20matter%20of%20time%20before%20people%20started%20decking%20out%20their%20Oura%20Rings%20%E2%80%94%20which%20first%20hit%20the%20market%20in%202015%20%E2%80%94%20with%20accessories.%20After%20all%2C%20everyone%20from%20Nike%20to%20Herm%C3%A8s%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20take%20a%20bite%20of%20the%20wearables%20market%20by%20developing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-watch-series-7-accessories%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EApple%20Watch%20accessories%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20Oura%20Ring%20jackets%20aren't%20a%20brand-new%20concept%20%E2%80%94%20you%20can%20spend%20%249%20and%20buy%20one%20on%20Amazon%20%E2%80%94%20what%20is%20new%20is%20that%20consumers%20are%20increasingly%20willing%20to%20spend%20thousands%20to%20make%20their%20health%20tech%20feel%20a%20little%20more%20like%20high%20fashion.%20Google%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esearches%20for%20%26quot%3BOura%20Ring%20jacket%26quot%3B%20spiked%20at%20the%20end%20of%202025%20after%20being%20practically%20nonexistent%20over%20the%20previous%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20trend%20is%20kicking%20off%20as%20the%20Oura%20Ring%20has%20garnered%20a%20cult%20following%2C%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foura-ring-fitness-tracker-pros-cons-after-years-wearing-style-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erings%20are%20becoming%20more%20ubiquitous%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20company%2C%20which%20is%20privately%20held%20and%20based%20in%20Finland%2C%20said%20in%20September%20that%20it%20was%20on%20track%20to%20reach%20%241%20billion%20in%20sales%20in%202025%2C%20doubling%20its%20revenues%20from%20the%20year%20before%2C%20and%20expects%20to%20hit%20%241.5%20billion%20in%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOura%20did%20not%20provide%20further%20comment%20when%20contacted%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20renderings%20of%20a%20gold%20diamond-encrusted%20Oura%20Ring%20Jacket%20against%20a%20white%20background%20showing%20the%20jewelry%20from%20different%20angles%2C%20including%20with%20a%20rendered%20Oura%20Ring.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ba8dd1ebc245a53a8115da%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221350%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHenri%20No%C3%ABl's%20Diamond%20Bubble%20Oura%20Jacket%20(%246%2C495)%20slips%20on%20top%20of%20an%20Oura%20Ring.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Henri%20No%C3%ABl%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dc74794b-9698-4345-87f8-1e85148376d6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%2410%2C000%20diamond%20encrusted%20jackets%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Oura%20Ring%20has%20evolved%20since%20its%202015%20debut%2C%20when%20it%20was%20made%20of%20ceramic%20steel%2C%20came%20in%20black%20and%20white%2C%20and%20resembled%20a%20chunky%20wedding%20band.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20generation%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Foura-ring-4-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20Oura%20Ring%204%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20made%20of%20titanium.%20It's%20sleeker%20and%20more%20expensive%20%E2%80%94%20the%20price%20starts%20at%20%24349%2C%20with%20gold%20and%20rose%20gold%20finishes%20at%20%24499.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20made%20attempts%20to%20make%20its%20rings%20feel%20more%20like%20fashion%20than%20tech%20over%20the%20years.%20It%20teamed%20up%20with%20Gucci%20in%202022%20on%20a%20%24950%20design%20with%20a%20braided%20border%20and%2018-karat%20gold%20Gucci%20G%2C%20and%20in%20October%2C%20released%20%24499%20ceramic%20versions%20of%20the%20Oura%20Ring%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20some%20wearers%2C%20it's%20still%20not%20glamorous%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20design%20is%20very%20functional%20and%20not%20all%20that%20elegant%2C%20so%20it's%20not%20surprising%20that%20businesses%20that%20help%20to%20boujify%20them%20have%20seen%20rapid%20growth%2C%26quot%3B%20Neil%20Saunders%2C%20managing%20director%20of%20GlobalData%20Retail%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20want%20something%20beautiful%2C%20personal%2C%20and%20made%20to%20fit%20into%20the%20way%20they%20live%20and%20what%20they%20wear%20every%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Henri%20No%C3%ABl%20founder%20Grimes%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOctavia%20Zamagias%2C%20founder%20of%20Octavia%20Elizabeth%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebased%20in%20West%20Hollywood%2C%20saw%20these%20jackets%20as%20a%20new%20business%20opportunity%20when%20she%20started%20to%20notice%20how%20popular%20the%20Oura%20Rings%20were.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20myself%20have%20worn%20one%20for%20a%20year%20and%20have%20so%20many%20friends%20into%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Oura%20itself%20is%2C%20to%20me%2C%20a%20bit%20of%20an%20eyesore%2C%20so%20to%20jazz%20it%20up%20with%20some%20diamonds%20felt%20like%20a%20must.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20expensive%20jackets%20she%20has%20sold%20cost%20just%20under%20%2410%2C000%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Oura%20ring%20jacket%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69babd80d387710cb9e45d6d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BChic%20and%20Shiny%20Initial%20Oura%20Ring%20Jacket%26quot%3B%20by%2024kt%20Concierge%20is%20made%20of%20solid%20gold.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jenya%20Srour%20at%2024kt%20Concierge%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJenya%20Srour%2C%20founder%20and%20chief%20designer%20of%2024kt%20Concierge%2C%20based%20in%20North%20Miami%2C%20decided%20to%20make%20an%20Oura%20Ring%20jacket%20for%20herself%20after%20buying%20the%20tech%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20something%20to%20track%20my%20wellness%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Srour.%20%26quot%3BI%20kept%20seeing%20it%20on%20people%2C%20and%20I%20thought%2C%20'wow%2C%20that's%20not%20a%20pretty%20piece%20of%20jewelry%20%E2%80%94%20we%20have%20to%20make%20them%20pretty.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20making%20a%20couple%20of%20adjustments%20to%20the%20first%20model%2C%20she%20launched%20the%20%243%2C980%20Confetti-themed%20Oura%20Ring%20jacket%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20jewelry%20designers%2C%20just%20like%20me%2C%20saw%20the%20growing%20popularity%20of%20something%20functional%20that%20we%20wanted%20to%20make%20beautiful%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20Srour%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20now%20has%20three%20jackets%20for%20sale%2C%20starting%20at%20%242%2C680.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20been%20really%20exciting%2C%26quot%3B%20Srour%20added.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20been%20lots%20of%20inquiries.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20fine%20jewelers%20making%20these%20jackets%20%E2%80%94%20Amazon%20and%20Etsy%20are%20full%20of%20Oura%20Ring%20accessories%2C%20some%20for%20as%20little%20as%20%249%2C%20including%20%26quot%3Bstacking%20rings%26quot%3B%20that%20are%20designed%20to%20be%20worn%20on%20either%20side%20of%20the%20Oura%20Ring%20to%20make%20it%20look%20more%20fashionable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20cite%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40thekerriesmart%2Fvideo%2F7498937522358078726%5C%22%20data-video-id%3D%5C%227498937522358078726%5C%22%3E%20%3Csection%3E%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22%40thekerriesmart%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40thekerriesmart%3Frefer%3Dembed%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%40thekerriesmart%3C%2Fa%3E%20Did%20you%20add%20sparkle%20ring%20bands%20to%20your%20%40ouraring%20Yes!%20I%20picked%20them%20up%20on%20Amazon%20and%20it%20looks%20so%20cute.%20You%20can%20find%20the%20exact%20ones%20in%20my%20storefront%20%F0%9F%92%95%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22ouraring%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Ftag%2Fouraring%3Frefer%3Dembed%5