A%20Rui%20Zhang%2C%20Angela%20Yu%2C%20and%5CnShipeng%20Fan.%3Cp%3EStoReel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBeijing-based%20StoReel%20raised%20%2434%20million%20to%20build%20out%20its%20AI%20micro%20drama%20app.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EStoReel%20has%20creators%20make%20micro%20dramas%20using%20AI%2C%20which%20it%20says%20can%20produce%20better%20stories%20at%20a%20lower%20cost.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERead%20the%20pitch%20deck%20it%20used%20to%20raise%20its%20funding%20round.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhollywood-wants-to-capitalize-on-mini-vertical-dramas-reelshort-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMicro%20dramas%20are%20booming%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20one%20startup%20is%20betting%20AI%20can%20help%20make%20them%20more%20interactive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStoReel%20is%20a%20Beijing-based%20startup%20that%20distributes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-testing-mini-drama-feed-ai-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI-made%20micro%20dramas%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20its%20mobile%20app.%20It's%20also%20a%20platform%20that%20lets%20creators%20make%20series%20using%20AI%20characters%20and%20voices.%20StoReel%20makes%20most%20of%20its%20revenue%20in%20the%20US%2C%20but%20is%20present%20in%20a%20handful%20of%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20shared%20exclusively%20with%20Business%20Insider%20that%20it%20had%20raised%20%2434%20million%20in%20funding%20%E2%80%94%20%249%20million%20in%20seed%20capital%20led%20by%20Play%20Ventures%2C%20and%20%2425%20million%20in%20user%20acquisition%20financing%20from%20PVX%20Partners.%20In%20user%20acquisition%20financing%2C%20investors%20do%20not%20receive%20equity%20in%20the%20company.%20They%20earn%20a%20return%20through%20a%20share%20of%20the%20revenue%20produced%20by%20a%20defined%20set%20of%20new%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20investors%20in%20the%20new%20round%20include%20T-Accelerate%20Capital%2C%20Tirta%20Ventures%2C%20and%20The%20Venture%20Reality%20Fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20join%20a%20growing%20number%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhollywood-invests-micro-dramas-disney-fox-explore-the-format-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einvestors%20in%20the%20micro%20drama%3C%2Fa%3E%20space%2C%20generally%2C%20including%20Fox%20Entertainment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2251d9def5-0d34-4bad-992b-e0617b30f975%5C%22%3EStoReel%20says%20AI%20is%20well-suited%20to%20micro%20dramas%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMicro%20dramas%2C%20the%20short-episode%20series%20meant%20for%20watching%20on%20your%20phone%2C%20have%20taken%20off%20in%20popularity.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicro-dramas-face-reality-check-after-buzzy-us-arrival-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHigh%20customer%20acquisition%20costs%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20repetitive%2C%20trope-filled%20storylines%20have%20raised%20questions%20about%20their%20staying%20power%2C%20however.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStoReel's%20pitch%20is%20that%20it%20can%20produce%20series%20cheaply%20with%20AI%20while%20focusing%20on%20LGBTQ%2B%2C%20sci-fi%2C%20and%20fantasy%20stories%20that%20are%20less%20common%20on%20the%20leading%20micro%20drama%20apps.%20StoReel%20also%20has%20features%20that%20let%20audiences%20interact%20with%20the%20characters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStoReel%20says%20it%20can%20make%20an%20hourlong%20series%20for%20%2420%2C000%20to%20%2440%2C000%20each%20%E2%80%94%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20cost%20of%20micro%20dramas%20that%20use%20human%20actors%2C%20which%20run%20around%20%24150%2C000%20to%20%24200%2C000.%20StoReel%20is%20investing%20in%20productions%2C%20with%20funds%20going%20toward%20creative%20development%2C%20AI%20tools%2C%20and%20computing.%20Over%20time%2C%20the%20company%20hopes%20creators%20will%20produce%20dramas%20independently%20using%20its%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMicro%20dramas%20are%20very%20compatible%20with%20AI%2C%20because%20they're%20highly%20iterative%2C%20and%20they're%20very%20fast%2C%20and%20there's%20high%20volume%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Angela%20Yu%2C%20StoReel's%20co-CEO.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20really%20a%20big%20shift%20because%20we're%20no%20longer%20trying%20to%20scale%20content%20linearly%2C%20like%20the%20traditional%20studio%20model.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStoReel%20invites%20creators%20%E2%80%94%20often%20recent%20film%20school%20grads%20%E2%80%94%20to%20develop%20series.%20They're%20paid%20on%20a%20minimum%20guarantee%20or%20a%20roughly%2050%25%20revenue%20share%20of%20subscription%20fees.%20Like%20most%20micro%20drama%20apps%2C%20StoReel%20makes%20money%20by%20charging%20viewers%20fees%20after%20several%20episodes%20%E2%80%94%20in%20its%20case%2C%20%2429.99%20a%20week%20and%20%24239.99%20a%20year%20for%20unlimited%20viewing.%20It%20plans%20to%20get%20deeper%20into%20advertising%20down%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20StoReel%20originates%20or%20fully%20funds%20the%20content%2C%20it%20often%20owns%20the%20IP.%20Over%20time%2C%20StoReel%20sees%20creators%20owning%20their%20IP%2C%20with%20the%20company%20providing%20distribution%20and%20monetization%20and%20getting%20platform%20exclusivity%20for%20a%20defined%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22afb281d7-062a-4c7a-87fa-1ad5948d7ca7%5C%22%3EStoReel%20says%20it's%20solving%20the%20content-cost%20problem%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPhylicia%20Koh%2C%20general%20partner%20at%20Play%20Ventures%2C%20said%20StoReel's%20AI%20lets%20creators%20experiment%20with%20new%20genres%20without%20as%20much%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20tend%20to%20complain%20about%20how%20it's%20always%20the%20same%20tropes%2C%26quot%3B%20Koh%20said%20of%20micro%20dramas.%20%26quot%3BThose%20are%20the%20things%20that%20the%20micro%20drama%20companies%20know%20get%20attention.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKoh%20said%20StoReel's%20model%20%26quot%3Breduces%20the%20cost%20of%20failure.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStoReel%20isn't%20the%20first%20in%20the%20space%20to%20use%20AI.%20For%20example%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.holywater.tech%2Fblog%2Fukrainian-company-holywater-has-launched-my-muse----an-ai-powered-generator-of-series-and-audiobooks-how-does-it-work-and-why-do-we-need-it-zapitati-v-chatgpt%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFox-backed%20Holywater%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year%20launched%20My%20Muse%2C%20an%20AI%20generator%20of%20series%20and%20audiobooks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYu%20said%20when%20StoReel%20made%20its%20first%20AI%20show%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20it%20was%20an%20%26quot%3Butter%20failure.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20very%20beginning%2C%20we%20were%20still%20a%20little%20bit%20nervous%2C%20hoping%20that%20it%20can%20perform%20at%20the%20same%20level%20as%20live%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BNow%20we've%20proven%20that%20as%20long%20as%20the%20genres%20and%20the%20story%20are%20unique%2C%20it%20doesn't%20matter%20if%20it's%20AI%20or%20if%20it's%20humans.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStoReel%20will%20also%20cancel%20a%20show%20early%20if%20it%20doesn't%20perform%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStoReel%20has%20posted%2059%20series%20on%20the%20platform.%20One%20of%20its%20biggest%20hits%20is%20%26quot%3BBrothers%20By%20Chance%2C%20Lovers%20By%20Choice%2C%26quot%3B%20about%20a%20couple%20who%20later%20become%20stepbrothers%20when%20their%20parents%20marry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYu%20is%20bullish%20on%20StoReel's%20interactivity%20because%20of%20the%20user%20behavior%20she%20observed%20at%20a%20Chinese%20AI%20companionship%20app%20where%20she%20previously%20worked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20really%20saw%20very%20high%20retention%2C%20because%20fans%20have%20an%20emotional%20need%20to%20chat%20with%2C%20kind%20of%20their%20fantasy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20people%20watch%20short%20dramas%2C%20it's%20also%20a%20type%20of%20escape.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESee%20the%20investor%20deck%20that%20StoReel%20used%20to%20raise%20its%20funding%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EStoReel%20pitches%20itself%20as%20an%20AI-native%20platform%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221594%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22StoReel%20pitch%20deck%201%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c192df5b58f1f0f9336596%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22876%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EStoReel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20app%20describes%20itself%20as%20a%20content%20platform%20where%20creators%20can%20make%20stories%20that%20scale%2C%20in%20contrast%20with%20traditional%20media%20companies%20that%20face%20increasing%20content%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIts%20deck%20introduces%20the%20StoReel%20team%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221570%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22StoReel%20pitch%20deck%202%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c1930258b5806618e7d894%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22862%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EStoReel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20it%20describes%20the%20cofounders%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ERui%20Zhang%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20CFO%2C%20and%20CFO%3Cbr%3EMaster's%20from%20Peking%20University%2C%20HSBC%20Business%20School.%20Managed%20over%20%24100M%20investments%20at%20INCE%20Capital%20and%20Hello%20Group%20specializing%20in%20consumer%20tech%20%26amp%3B%20AI%20sectors.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EShipeng%20Fan%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20CEO%3Cbr%3EMaster's%20from%20Peking%20University.%20Led%20short%20drama%20division%20at%20Linmon%20Pictures%20%E2%80%94%20a%20leading%20publicly%20listed%20TV%20studio%20in%20China.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EAngela%20Yu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20co-CEO%3Cbr%3EColumbia%20Business%20School%2C%20MBA.%20Product%20lead%20of%20AI%20companionship%20app%20at%20Hello%20Group%20-%200%20to%201%20scaling%20to%204M%2B%20users.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESt