s.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-outlook-sp500-correction-goldman-sachs-bonds-investing-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ES%26amp%3BP%20500%3C%2Fa%3E%20crossed%20below%20its%20200-day%20moving%20average%20last%20week%20as%20the%20benchmark%20index%20continues%20to%20struggle%20in%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it's%20not%20always%20a%20sure%20sign%20that%20a%20bear%20market%20is%20on%20the%20way%2C%20it's%20a%20potentially%20worrying%20signal%20that%20the%20market%20could%20be%20headed%20into%20a%20downward%20trend%20in%20the%20months%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20technical%20level%20has%20historically%20been%20crossed%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20every%20bear%20market%20since%20at%20least%202000%2C%20according%20to%20an%20analysis%20by%20Lance%20Roberts%2C%20the%20chief%20investment%20strategist%20at%20RIA%20Advisors%2C%20which%20oversees%20around%20%242%20billion%20in%20assets.%20During%20those%20episodes%2C%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20has%20ended%20up%2C%20on%20average%2C%204.8%25%20lower%20six%20months%20after%20the%20moving%20average%20was%20crossed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FY5y4f%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Line%20chart%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FY5y4f%2Ffull.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EStocks%20have%20endured%20a%20rough%20few%20months%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-war-strait-of-hormuz-stock-market-shipping-oil-prices-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esurging%20oil%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjobs-report-february-data-live-updates-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eweak%20jobs%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20sticky%20inflation%2C%20and%20AI%20disruption%20have%20derailed%20investors'%20optimism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20do%20you%20know%20if%20things%20are%20going%20to%20keep%20getting%20worse%20for%20stocks%3F%20Well%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20watch%20for%20updates%20to%20the%20market's%20fundamental%20drivers%20%E2%80%94%20the%20issues%20listed%20above.%20But%20technical%20indicators%20can%20also%20offer%20clues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20report%20on%20Monday%2C%20Roberts%20laid%20out%20a%20checklist%20of%20six%20criteria%20to%20watch%20for%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20200-day%20moving%20average%20is%20still%20moving%20downward%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20moving%20average%20convergence%2Fdivergence%20indicator%20is%20dipping%20into%20negative%20territory%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20index's%20relative%20strength%20index%20is%20below%2032%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAmerican%20Association%20of%20Individual%20Investors'%20sentiment%20survey%20shows%20at%20least%2045%25%20of%20investors%20are%20bearish%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMore%20than%2040%25%20of%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20stocks%20are%20trading%20below%20their%20200-day%20moving%20averages%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20200-day%20moving%20average%20has%20crossed%20below%20the%2050-day%20moving%20average%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20now%2C%20only%20two%20of%20those%20things%20are%20true%2C%20Roberts%20said%3A%2046%25%20of%20stocks%20are%20trading%20below%20their%20200-day%20moving%20average%2C%20and%20the%20moving%20average%20convergence%2Fdivergence%20indicator%20is%20still%20falling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20it's%20still%20too%20early%20to%20know%20how%20the%20market%20will%20fare%2C%20Roberts%20said%2C%20but%20it's%20still%20important%20to%20prepare%20your%20portfolio%20for%20near-term%20downside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2255f0265b-1719-4734-ba1d-4336de3f306d%5C%22%3E6%20steps%20to%20protect%20your%20portfolio%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20shared%20several%20steps%20for%20taking%20risk%20off%20the%20table%2C%20starting%20with%20%3Cstrong%3Etrimming%20your%20largest%20positions%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReduce%20concentration%20in%20your%20highest-valuation%2C%20highest-conviction%20holdings%20by%2020%20to%2030%20percent%2C%26quot%3B%20Roberts%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20not%20betting%20against%20recovery%20%E2%80%94%20you're%20limiting%20the%20damage%20from%20a%20potential%2012%20to%2015%20percent%20further%20drawdown%20before%20the%20low%20is%20confirmed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHand-in-hand%20with%20that%20recommendation%20is%20to%20%3Cstrong%3Ehold%20at%20least%2010%25-15%25%20of%20your%20portfolio%20in%20cash%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20That%20way%2C%20you'll%20have%20money%20waiting%20on%20the%20sidelines%20waiting%20to%20buy%20if%20stocks%20go%20lower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThird%2C%20Roberts%20said%20to%20%3Cstrong%3Elean%20more%20into%20the%20quality%20factor%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20and%20less%20into%20growth%20stocks.%20Characteristics%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20quality%20stock%20include%20a%20pricing%20power%2C%20a%20strong%20balance%20sheet%2C%20and%20high%20free%20cash%20flow%20levels.%20The%20Vanguard%20U.S.%20Quality%20Factor%20ETF%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fetfs%2Fvanguard-us-quality-factor-etf-shares-us9219357061%3FmiRedirects%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EVFQY%3C%2Fa%3E)%20is%20one%20example%20of%20a%20fund%20offering%20exposure%20to%20quality%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFourth%2C%20%3Cstrong%3Eup%20your%20allocation%20to%20the%20utilities%2C%20healthcare%2C%20and%20consumer%20staples%20sectors%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20as%20they've%20historically%20behaved%20defensively%20when%20the%20broader%20market%20and%20economy%20is%20in%20trouble.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFifth%2C%20for%20more%20volatile%20stocks%20like%20cyclicals%2C%20%3Cstrong%3Eadjust%20your%20stop-losses%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20to%20allow%20for%20downside%20of%20just%207%25-10%25%2C%20Roberts%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20finally%2C%20%3Cstrong%3Emove%20up%20the%20average%20duration%20of%20your%20Treasury%20exposure%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20to%20the%20five-to-seven%20year%20range%2C%20Roberts%20said.%20Yields%20are%20higher%20there%20than%20at%20the%20short%20end%20of%20the%20yield%20curve%2C%20and%20medium-and-longer%20duration%20bonds%20tend%20to%20increase%20in%20value%20if%20the%20economy%20starts%20to%20falter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-volatility-200dma-iran-war-how-to-protect-portfolio-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774430101000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c2c23be98a37a4841f318a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-volatility-200dma-iran-war-how-to-protect-portfolio-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20crossed%20below%20its%20200-day%20moving%20average%20last%20week%2C%20a%20signal%20that%20the%20benchmark%20index%20could%20be%20headed%20into%20a%20downward%20trend.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22wedwards%40businessinsider.com%20(William%20Edwards)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-volatility-200dma-iran-war-how-to-protect-portfolio-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Iranian%20former%20commander%20who%20could%20be%20Trump's%20pick%20to%20negotiate%20with%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774430100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F26%2F03%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-qalibaf-iran_7202552.jpg%3F20260325103409%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fthe-iranian-former-commander-who-could-be-trumps-pick-to-negotiate-with-13524167%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20former%20commander%20of%20Iran's%20Revolutionary%20Guards%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20possible%20US%20contact%20for%20talks%20-%20as%20the%20new%20Supr