%26quot%3B%20helped%20the%20transformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Intrator%2C%20the%20company's%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%2C%20said%20CoreWeave's%20early%20days%20in%20crypto%20gave%20it%20an%20edge%20in%20understanding%20how%20to%20use%20GPUs%2C%20the%20chips%20now%20powering%20the%20AI%20boom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20pretty%20nerdy%2C%20we%20dig%20under%20the%20hood%2C%26quot%3B%20Intrator%20said%20on%20an%20episode%20of%20the%20All-In%20podcast%20recorded%20at%20Nvidia's%20GTC%20conference%20and%20released%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECoreWeave%20started%20by%20mining%20Ethereum%20and%20weathered%20multiple%20crypto%20downturns%2C%20including%20the%202018%20crash%20that%20sent%20Bitcoin%20tumbling%20from%20nearly%20%2420%2C000%20to%20around%20%243%2C000%20in%20just%2012%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20weathered%20crypto%20winter%20really%20well%20and%20immediately%20started%20to%20look%20for%20other%20use%20cases%2C%26quot%3B%20Intrator%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20approach%20%E2%80%94%20treating%20computing%20power%20as%20flexible%20infrastructure%20rather%20than%20a%20single-purpose%2C%20crypto-focused%20bet%20%E2%80%94%20positioned%20the%20company%20to%20capitalize%20when%20demand%20for%20AI%20surged%20after%20the%20release%20of%20ChatGPT%20in%202022.%20Today%2C%20CoreWeave%20sells%20large-scale%20GPU%20capacity%20to%20AI%20companies%20and%20cloud%20providers%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.coreweave.com%2Fblog%2Fwhat-makes-coreweave-the-first-true-ai-hyperscaler-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecalls%20itself%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20%26quot%3Bfirst%20true%20hyperscaler.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20rapidly%20scaled%20alongside%20that%20demand%2C%20raising%20tens%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20to%20finance%20its%20infrastructure%20buildout.%20Its%20market%20capitalization%20was%20%2443.6%20billion%20as%20of%20Tuesday%20afternoon%2C%20according%20to%20Yahoo%20Finance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20investors%20are%20skeptical%20of%20the%20model%2C%20which%20relies%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoreweave-stock-blue-owl-capital-data-center-financing-ai-crwv-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eheavily%20on%20debt%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20fund%20expansion.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoreweave-stock-short-seller-report-kerrisdale-ai-nvidia-gpus-tech-2025-9%3Futm_source%3Dchatgpt.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKerrisdale%20Capital%20took%20a%20short%20position%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20CoreWave%20last%20year%2C%20saying%20the%20company%20%26quot%3Bisn't%20pioneering%20the%20future%20of%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20a%20debt-fueled%20GPU%20rental%20business%20with%20no%20moat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20publicly%20pushed%20back%2C%20including%20with%20the%20launch%20of%20its%20first%20major%20ad%20campaign%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-ai-company-coreweave-chance-the-rapper-marketing-push-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estarring%20Chance%20the%20Rapper%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20called%20%26quot%3BReady%20for%20anything%2C%20ready%20for%20AI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIntrator%20is%20also%20pushing%20back.%20In%20the%20Monday%20interview%2C%20he%20described%20the%20company%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Binnovator%26quot%3B%20in%20how%20it%20finances%20its%20operations.%20He%20described%20a%20structure%20that%20bundles%20customer%20contracts%2C%20GPUs%2C%20and%20data%20center%20agreements%20into%20a%20single%20vehicle%20that%20governs%20cash%20flow.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoreweave-nvidia-gaurantee-data-center-leases-financing-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECustomers%20like%20Nvidia%20and%20Microsoft%3C%2Fa%3E%20pay%20into%20the%20structure%2C%20which%20then%20covers%20costs%20like%20power%2C%20debt%2C%20and%20operations%20before%20returning%20profits%20to%20CoreWeave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20called%20a%20box%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20what's%20important%20to%20understand%20is%20the%20economics%20in%20this%20box%20are%20such%20that%20within%202.5%20years%20of%20a%20five-year%20deal%2C%20we%20have%20paid%20for%20everything.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoreweave-ceo-nerdy-pivot-crypto-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774429621000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c2eac15b58f1f0f9336bfb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoreweave-ceo-nerdy-pivot-crypto-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Michael%20Intrator%2C%20CoreWeave's%20CEO%2C%20helped%20steer%20the%20company%20away%20from%20crypto%20after%20major%20%26quot%3Bwinters.%26quot%3B%20It's%20now%20worth%20nearly%20%2450%20billion.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bshimkus%40insider.com%20(Ben%20Shimkus)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoreweave-ceo-nerdy-pivot-crypto-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I'm%20a%20former%20magazine%20editor%20who%20wakes%20up%20every%20day%20at%205%3A17%20a.m.%20for%20good%20luck.%20Here's%20a%20day%20in%20my%20new%20flexible%20life%20as%20a%20mom%20of%203.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223335%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Liz%20Plosser%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b9b7e275bee4e0ee55d64e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELiz%20Plosser%2C%20the%20former%20editor-in-chief%20of%20Women's%20Health%2C%20now%20runs%20a%20Substack%20and%20YouTube%20channel%20in%20addition%20to%20her%20freelance%20consulting%20work.%3Cp%3ELiz%20Plosser%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Liz%20Plosser%2C%20